Sphere: Mind Sphere<br/><br/>
<br/><br/>
Usage leaving (direction)<br/><br/>
<br/>
This spell will magically transport you out of a combat, taking you to an<br/>
adjoining room in the direction specified.  If the room you are in does not<br/>
link to another room in the direction which you specify the spell will fail.<br/>
